data.description: OFFERING $20,000 Buy down credit for buyers at purchase price of $565,000. Assumable VA LOAN AT 3.5%!!! Welcome Home to 3608 Red Feather Trail, Cheyenne, Wyoming! Nestled in the heart of Cheyenne's serene and friendly community, this charming home is the epitome of comfort and convenience. Offering a perfect blend of modern elegance and cozy living, 3608 Red Feather Trail is the dream abode you've been searching for. This open ranch floor plan with a main floor master and a main floor laundry! Amazing features throughout! Smart home with auto blinds, water sensors, smart thermostat, Smart lights. HOA mows the lawn and shovels the snow!  Check out this home today! $2,500 lender credit available if financed with Dominick Romig of Fairway Mortgage. Inquire with listing agent for details!
